                     special_linear (by W. Stein)

EXAMPLES:
    sage: G = Sp(4,GF(7))
    sage: G._gap_init_()
    'Sp(4, 7)'
    sage: G
    Symplectic Group of rank 2 over Finite Field of size 7
    sage: G.random_element()
    [1 0 5 6]
    [0 5 2 4]
    [4 0 2 3]
    [3 6 2 0]
    sage: G.order()
    276595200

"""

